&lt;p data-start=&quot;143&quot; data-end=&quot;310&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;143&quot; data-end=&quot;165&quot;&gt;Habilidades clave:&lt;/strong&gt; Arquitectura Empresarial, TOGAF, Zachman, BIAN, BPM, RPA, IA Agéntica (LLM, RAG), Microservicios, Docker, Kubernetes, SOA, REST, OAuth2, Cloud&lt;/p&gt;
